                     <interp inst="t18470705-1578-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="stealingFromMaster"></interp> for stealing 1 blunderbuss, value 1<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 5<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; the goods of <persName id="t18470705-name-170" type="victimName">
